17 Aug 2015 Sierra Leone: LSTM [Liverpool School of Tropical Medicine]'s CMNH [Centre for Maternal and Newborn Health] raises funds for Ebola-hit maternal health facilities in Sierra Leone
http://www.news-medical.net/news/20150817/LSTMs-CMNH-raises-funds-for-Ebola-hit-maternal-health-facilities-in-Sierra-Leone.aspx

